Like other merchants, Enron plunged into California after the legislature op=
ened up that giant state to electricity competition. But the Southeast remai=
ned less-friendly territory.=20
Texas is the only southern state to adopt retail deregulation. Florida goes =
so far as to ban out-of-state companies from building almost any plant for t=
he wholesale market.=20
